history.content:
I'm currently taking 61a and 16a, and next semester will take 61b. I'm not sure whether it is more useful to take cs70 in the fall and declare earlier or take 16b first since I'll still have priority enrollment (I'm a current freshman). I don't want to take all three at once since I'm also going to be taking a breadth on top of this.

Another option would be to take 61bl over the summer, but since I'm planning to double major with Cognitive Science, I'm taking already going to take data 8 to declare. However, I took AP Stat in high school and got a 5, so would it be doable to take 61b and data 8 together?
history.subject: EECS 16B vs CS 70 for fall?
